35:28.927 --> 35:36.234 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: The Hardee's in
Maysville, Kentucky,
a popular hangout for the senior
set.

35:36.267 --> 35:40.438 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
