36:05.530 --> 36:07.332 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
But why?

36:07.365 --> 36:12.303 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGUS DEATON, Economist: The
health crisis
here is particularly among white
working-class

36:12.337 --> 36:15.206 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
or white people with a high
school and no
more.

36:15.240 --> 36:20.245 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For those people, the economy's
been very
hard for a very long time.

36:20.278 --> 36:24.349 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Predictably, Angus
Deaton and
Anne Case, economists who have
documented

36:24.382 --> 36:29.654 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the dramatic decrease in life
expectancy,
say an obvious place to look for
a cause is

36:29.687 --> 36:31.322 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the economy.

36:31.356 --> 36:33.425 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
