your family.

36:36.428 --> 36:41.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And the disappearance of those
may lead people
to feel a lot more stressed.

36:41.666 --> 36:49.107 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Indeed, in the
period covered
by their study, 1999-2014,
inflation-adjusted

36:49.140 --> 36:55.814 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
